    {
      "id": "sybil_23_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_23",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with practicality. The exterior finish retains a high gloss, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips and faint surface marks consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable and clean environment; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and all electronic features, including the infotainment and climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust\u2014I have strictly followed the manufacturer\u2019s service schedule, and the engine runs smoothly without any leaks or odd noises. Recent service includes a full synthetic oil change, a fresh set of premium all-season tires, and a brake pad replacement. It drives straight and true, offering a quiet, composed ride. This is a turnkey car for someone who wants reliability and a sharp appearance without the new-car price tag.",
